snippet.title: Paper Cut Mansion - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Paper Cut Mansion is set to be released on October 27 and this launch trailer will showcase the game in action and the fully voiced musical soundtrack. Paper Cut Mansion is a Roguelite Horror set in a cardboard universe. The player is a paper man trapped in a paper mansion who has to solve a series of puzzles and riddles “escape-room” style in order to get out of the house.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
